Value Added Service Tempalates nomenclature

Templates of a one time/reapeadable value added service
that can be add on contract signing.

place: 
Administration / VAS Templates

----------------------------------------------------------------------
examples: 

name: Installtion Fee,  price: 20.00, one time
name: WIFI router sell, price: 35.00, one time
name: Repeating charge, price: 5.00 , three times
name: Loayal customer discount, price: 2.00 , livetime, montly bill discount
